{"word":"G1832 - ἔξεστι - éxesti - ex'-es-tee - Be lawful","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἔξεστι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">éxesti</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ex'-es-tee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be lawful</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தகுந்த, நியாயமான, அதிகாரம்"},{"paragraph":"it is lawful"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Third person singular present indicative of a compound of <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G1510 - εἰμί - eimí - i-mee'/1510\">G1510</a>; so also <b>&#x03B5;&#x0313;&#x03BE;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03BD;</b> <b>exon</b>; neuter present participle of the same (with or without some form of <a href=\"#/G1510 - εἰμί - eimí - i-mee'/1510\">G1510</a> expressed); impersonally <i>it is right</i> (through the figurative idea of <i>being out</i> in public): - be lawful, let, X may (-est).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1832/1832\">G1832</a>, <a href=\"#/G1849/1849\">G1849</a>, <a href=\"#/G1850/1850\">G1850</a>, <a href=\"#/G2715/2715\">G2715</a>"}]}